Leaflet.zoomslider
==================

### Description
A zoom slider widget for [Leaflet][2]

Tested with Chrome, IE 7-9 and Firefox. 

Also see [Leaflet.Pancontrol][1]

[1]: https://github.com/kartena/Leaflet.Pancontrol
[2]: https://github.com/CloudMade/Leaflet
